ğŸ§  STEP 1 â€“ What is LWC

Lightning Web Components (LWC) = Salesforceâ€™s modern front-end framework built on standard JavaScript, HTML, and CSS.

It lets you create fast, reusable UI components that talk to Salesforce data using Apex or built-in wire adapters.

Think of LWC as the â€œvisual faceâ€ of your Apex logic.

